reviewText: The Fluidity Fitness Beginner Workout DVD is a great place to start to learn the Fluidity Moves and get comfortable working with the bar. I recommend it to anyone. Fluidity Barre System with Bonus Seat & Thigh DVD, Silver/Blue

I was real please with videos

  Karen hack
Sve you money and go to the gym. They exercises were boring and I only did the video a few times.
I really like the work out and the bar.  After using it about a month others are making comments and asking if I have lost weight!!!
For the price of the video I thought I was getting the equipment also!!!! It's true what they say......Live and learn
This work out is just what I was looking for. No high impact but a great impact on your body

I knew this was the kind of exercise that I needed with my degenerative disc and joint disease. It really is fluid and kind to my back and joints. I take it easy and don't rush what I do when moving along with this video. Since I started my pain meds are lasting longer and I sleep longer without pain waking me up. As time goes by, I can see where my back and legs will become stronger.

The product was shipped quickly and in perfect condition.
